reviewText: Just a few different scenes than the best of Jenny Mccarthy, so don't buy both. But I say this is a good buy for J.M. fans.

Just take a look at the cover of the box and you'll see a perfect woman, she's worth a look. Jenny McCarthy combines perfection, erotism and talent, and in this DVD she's more than that. Check all the images of her and you understand why she was elected PMOY 1994. There's no waste of time and money with this DVD. BUY IT!
